{"tha-ap303:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap303:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap303:0.3":"Padumakesariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap303:1.1":"“Isisanghe aham pubbe, ","tha-ap303:1.2":"asim matangavarano; ","tha-ap303:1.3":"Mahesinam pasadena, ","tha-ap303:1.4":"padmakesaramokirim. ","tha-ap303:2.1":"Paccekajinasetthesu, ","tha-ap303:2.2":"dhutaragesu tadisu; ","tha-ap303:2.3":"Tesu cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap303:2.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap303:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap303:3.2":"kesaram okirim tada; ","tha-ap303:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap303:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap303:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap303:4.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap303:4.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap303:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap303:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padumakesariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap303:6.1":"Padumakesariyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}